<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.9.6">
<l>peṇmaimiku vaṭivukoṭu vantavaḷaip periya pēyiṉatu ruvukoṭu māḷavuyi ruṇṭu</l>
<l>tiṇmaimiku marutoṭunaṟ cakaṭamiṟut taruḷun tēvaṉavaṉ makiḻntiṉitu maruviyuṟai kōyil</l>
<l>uṇmaimiku maṟaiyoṭunaṟ kalaikaṇiṟai poṟaika ḷutavukoṭai yeṉṟivaṟṟi ṉoḻivillā periya</l>
<l>vaṇmaimiku maṟaiyavarkaḷ maliveytu nāṅkūr vaikunta viṇṇakaram vaṇaṅkumaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Simple heart, worship in Vaikunta Viṇṇakaram in Nānkūr which acquires</l>
<l rend="indent">the best of Vedic experts whose great praises increase</l>
<l>Without ceasing in these: the Vedas which abound in truth, refined</l>
<l rend="indent">scholarship, many [types of] meditations, and giving of aid,</l>
<l>The temple where dwells the deity, happily with affection [and] rejoicing,</l>
<l rend="indent">who was gracious, breaking the marutu trees,</l>
<l rend="indent">whose strength was great, and the cruel cart,</l>
<l>Having consumed the life of the one who came with a form like a woman</l>
<l rend="indent">so that [she] perished with the shape of a huge demon.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
